| Trit | Role | Repos |
|------|------|-------|
| -1 (MINUS) | Infrastructure | MCP servers, bafishka, CategoricalTowers |
| 0 (ERGODIC) | Bridges | Gay.jl, GeoACSets, agent-o-shiva |
| +1 (PLUS) | Applications | multiverse-color-game, gay-hy, xf.jl |
\stopverb}
}

\subtree{
\title{Key Insights}
\ol{
\li{\strong{Parametrised Optics} - bmorphism's bio references jules-hedges' work on cybernetic systems}
\li{\strong{Topological Chemputer} - plurigrid/asi connects Cronin's chemputer to categorical systems}
\li{\strong{UnwiringDiagrams} - Fork of AlgebraicJulia for "Uexküll Umweltung" (environment-world)}
\li{\strong{MCP Constellation} - Multiple MCP servers forming distributed tool network}
}
}

